      "author_association" : "NONE",
      "body" : "> Speaking of hard forks, wonder how /u/luke-jr is doing on the 2MB hard fork code that was promised to miners within the next 10 days. Greg Maxwell incredibly hasn't the slightest idea about the progress of one of Blockstream's contractors and his fellow developer.\n> This was promised to miners many months ago. Can't wait to see another empty promise broken.\n\n[Reddit Comment](https://www.reddit.com/r/btc/comments/4tvw5y/hardforks_did_you_know/d5kr222)\n\n@luke-jr Is that correct or just rumor? Will 2 MB blocksize come in 13.0 update?\n",
